                                <emph>Gajʾ ündeledoɣan orunda</emph>; unvocalized text. | H:
                                <emph>Gaj indeledoɣan orunda</emph>. | C: <emph>gajʾada</emph>. | R:
                                <emph>Gajʾda</emph>. | Heb. <foreign xml:lang="he"
